These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, orange, pumpkin, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, chess, drawing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rowing, tennis, handball
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person eating watermelon##6
 5. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person eating orange##8
 8. the person eating orange is not the person who's sport is handball##6
 9. the person eating grapefruit is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
10. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person eating orange is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
12. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
13. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
14. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | grapefruit         | watermelon     | pumpkin     | orange         |
| Hobby   | chess | camping    | drawing     | traveling |
| Sport   | swimming       | rowing | handball | tennis       |

