.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, almond-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, videographer, coach, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding, handball, rowing
 1. the coach is not to the right of the paramedic##8
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the videographer##1
 5. the firefighter is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the firefighter##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk          | 7up      | fanta      | cola   |
| Job        | coach     | firefighter | videographer | paramedic      |
| Sport      | rowing | snowboarding    | skateboarding  | handball |

