.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, woodworking, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, rock, folk, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bike, skateboard, bus
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is not the fan of jazz##6
 6. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking  | skydiving | gardening | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | jazz      | electronic | folk        |
| Transport     | scooter | skateboard       | bus    | bike     |

