.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, musical, comedy, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, electronic, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, polish, pakistani, dutch
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 2. the polish is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
 3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the pakistani is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
 7. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 9. the turkish is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the person watching drama movies is the pakistani##1
11. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | drama | musical    | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | salsa     | house   | classical     |
| Nationality   | turkish | pakistani   | polish | dutch    |

