The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, spy, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, weightlifting, handball, climbing
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person who's sport is handball##6
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is chess##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess       | skydiving | sudoku  | board-games    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy       | thriller    | musical | disaster    |
