.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, garlic, pineapple, lime
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, japanese, canadian
 1. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
 2. the person watching zombie movies is not the indonesian##6
 3. the japanese is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person watching zombie movies##7
 4. the indonesian is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 6. the japanese is the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 8. the canadian is between the person eating peas and the japanese##2
 9. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
10. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
11. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | garlic      | pineapple      | lime | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical    | zombie | martial-arts     |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | japanese | canadian  | indonesian |

