There 4 different types of food: cherry, kale, onion, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, indie, funk, techno
1. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person eating onion##7
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the fan of funk is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
5. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
7. the person eating watermelon is the fan of indie##1
8. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person drinking tea##7
9. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea     | water | sprite  | almond-milk |
| Food          | kale | watermelon   | cherry | onion |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | indie   | techno      | funk      |

