 1. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
 2. the spanish is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the argentine##7
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 4. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the american is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 7. the spanish is on the left or right of the american##3
 8. the american is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
10. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
11. the american is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
13. the american is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
14. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
