 4. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
 5. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
10. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
