4. the egyptian is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the french is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the turkish##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is tennis##7
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian     | turkish  | japanese |
| Pet           | ferret      | cat        | rat   | mouse |
| Sport         | tennis  | skateboarding | volleyball | parkour       |

 